m_assets/steam/apps/850880/extras/8557ef024c63d9965fed687873bc4e3e.mp4?t=1763609127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Become a Vegetaball champion, and use your psy powers to dominate the court. Use your mind to jump, dash, hit, shoot and score your way to victory.<br>Psy-KICK power drank misters will recharge your psy, and keep you energized for the whole game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/850880/extras/efad8a09c135a6b1d3e5d948ae933f24.poster.avif?t=1763609127\" width=620 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/850880/extras/efad8a09c135a6b1d3e5d948ae933f24.webm?t=1763609127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/850880/extras/efad8a09c135a6b1d3e5d948ae933f24.mp4?t=1763609127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Keep it fresh and switch between 6 challenging courts. Flash through \"The H\" or dominate the Warehouse.<br>Play on a team, or find the ultimate opponent in a duel. Relax with friends in the Sauna before the game.",
